    "description": "An advanced Graphical User Interface for the analysis of short and long read Human Leukocyte Antigen-typing data.\n\nHLAssign assigns known haplotypes to next-generation sequencing data from appropriate targeted enrichment panels (two analysis modes: PCR based, capture-based), allowing interactive quality control, manual selection of alternative haplotypes, and generation of a report in PDF or CSV format.\n\nFree software for HLA typing from targeted NGS data.",
